India’s RBI Defers Start of Credit Default Swap Guidelines

-- B y   H a r i   G o v i n d
-- 
2011-10-21T02:58:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/india-s-rbi-defers-start-of-credit-default-swap-guidelines.html
India ’s central bank has deferred
the start of credit default swaps guidelines for corporate
bonds, according to a statement posted on the website of the
Reserve Bank of India.  The new date will be “announced shortly,” the release
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
